    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make all drone pilots subject to licensing and create a register of owners",
        "additional_details": "Yet again we have flight delays due to irresponsible owners flying drones close to airports.  We have already had drones flying dangerously close to aircraft and, apart from the inconvenience that is experienced by the public due to this, it is a real threat to human life.",
        "background": "With the danger posed by some irresponsible drone pilots, the govt should pass laws to regulate purchases of these items, licence pilots after they have passed a proficiency test, have registration documents for each drone and have gps tracking fitted so that a flight log is maintained.",
